  "description": "Road traffic estimates by volume, vehicle type and road class in Great Britain, for the year ending March 2015. ",
  "details": {
    "body": "<div class=\"govspeak\">\n<p>Comparing the year to end March 2015 with the same period in 2014:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>all motor vehicle traffic increased by 1.8 %, to 312.4 billion vehicle miles</li>\n  <li>car traffic increased by 1.3 %</li>\n  <li>\n<abbr title=\"Light Goods Vehicles\">LGV</abbr> traffic increased by 5.1 %, reaching a new peak of 45.5 billion vehicle miles</li>\n  <li>traffic volumes increased across all road classifications</li>\n  <li>minor rural road traffic increased the most, rising 4.9 % to reach 44.1 billion vehicle miles</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"contact-us\">Contact us</h2>\n\n<div class=\"contact \" id=\"contact_1335\">\n  <div class=\"content\">\n <div class=\"vcard contact-inner\">\n\n  <p>Road traffic and vehicle speed statistics</p>\n\n <div class=\"email-url-number\">\n            <p class=\"email\">\n              <span class=\"type\">Email</span>\n              <a class=\"email\" href=\"mailto:roadtraff.stats@dft.gsi.gov.uk\">roadtraff.stats@dft.gsi.gov.uk</a>\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"tel\">\n              <span class=\"type\">Public enquiries</span>\n              020 7944 3095\n            </p>\n        </div>\n\n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n</div>",
